                <caption>Speech-to-Text pricing details and features by tie=
r</caption>
            </table>
            <div class=3D"row row-size1 column">
                <p class=3D"text-body5">
                    See the <a href=3D"https://docs.microsoft.com/zh-cn/azu=
re/cognitive-services/speech-service/speech-services-quotas-and-limits" ari=
a-label=3D"See the documentation for information on quotas,limits" data-bi-=
an=3D"body" data-bi-tn=3D"undefined">documentation</a> for information on q=
uotas, limits and <a href=3D"https://docs.microsoft.com/zh-cn/azure/cogniti=
ve-services/speech-service/speech-services-quotas-and-limits#speech-to-text=
-quotas-and-limits-per-speech-resource" aria-label=3D"Learn More about how =
to increase concurrent requests" data-bi-an=3D"body" data-bi-tn=3D"undefine=
d">instructions</a> on how to increase concurrent requests.
                </p>
                <p class=3D"text-body5">Speech to text hours are measured a=
s the hours of audio sent to the service, billed in second increments.</p>
                <p class=3D"text-body5"><sup>1</sup>To take advantage of th=
is new Batch Transcription pricing you need to use Speech to text REST API =
V3.2 or later versions. See <a href=3D"https://docs.microsoft.com/zh-cn/azu=
re/ai-services/speech-service/rest-speech-to-text" aria-label=3D"See Speech=
 to Text REST API documentation for details on Batch Transcription pricing =
using version 3.2 or later" data-bi-an=3D"body" data-bi-tn=3D"undefined">Sp=
eech to text REST API</a> for information.</p>
                <p class=3D"text-body5"><sup>2</sup>This reflects public pr=
eview pricing.</p>
                <p class=3D"text-body5"><sup>3</sup>This price includes 1 a=
udio input and output, up to 2 text translation language using standard or =
custom Speech to Text and standard Translation. For custom Translation or 3=
+ translation languages, please reference the <a href=3D"https://azure.micr=
osoft.com/zh-cn/pricing/details/translator/" aria-label=3D"Reference the Az=
ure AI Translator Text Translation pricing page for details on custom trans=
lation and three or more translation languages" data-bi-an=3D"body" data-bi=
-tn=3D"undefined">Azure Translator in Foundry Tools Text Translation pricin=
g page</a>.</p>
                <p class=3D"text-body5"><sup>4</sup>Selected text to speech=
 voices are available via two model variants: Neural and NeuralHD. Learn mo=
re <a href=3D"https://learn.microsoft.com/azure/ai-services/speech-service/=
high-definition-voices" aria-label=3D"Learn More about Neural and NeuralHD"=
 data-bi-an=3D"body" data-bi-tn=3D"undefined">here</a>.</p>
                <p class=3D"text-body5"><sup>5</sup>Custom Speech Training =
applies when customizing any base model released on or after October 1, 202=
3.</p>
                <p class=3D"text-body5"><sup>6</sup>Personal Voice is a lim=
ited access feature restricted to certain <a href=3D"https://aka.ms/Persona=
lVoiceUseCase" aria-label=3D"View pre-approved use cases for Personal Voice=
 limited access feature" data-bi-an=3D"body" data-bi-tn=3D"undefined">pre-a=
pproved use cases only</a>, with a need to <a href=3D"https://aka.ms/Person=
alVoiceForm" aria-label=3D"Apply for access to Personal Voice limited acces=
s feature" data-bi-an=3D"body" data-bi-tn=3D"undefined">applying for access=
</a>. To learn more about the service, <a href=3D"https://aka.ms/PersonalVo=
iceDocs" aria-label=3D"Check the document to learn more about Personal Voic=
e limited access feature and approved use cases" data-bi-an=3D"body" data-b=
i-tn=3D"undefined">check the document</a>.</p>
                <p class=3D"text-body5"><sup>7</sup>Text to Speech: speech =
synthesis usage is billed per character. Avatar is billed per second. Train=
ing and model hosting is billed per second.</p>
                <p class=3D"text-body5"><sup>8</sup>To use Fast Transcripti=
on you need to use Speech to text REST API 2024-11-15 or later versions. Se=
e <a href=3D"https://docs.microsoft.com/zh-cn/azure/ai-services/speech-serv=
ice/rest-speech-to-text" aria-label=3D"See Speech to Text REST API document=
ation for details on Fast Transcription using version 2024-05-15-preview or=
 later" data-bi-an=3D"body" data-bi-tn=3D"undefined">Speech to text REST AP=
I</a> for information.</p>
                <p class=3D"text-body5"><sup>9</sup>LLM Speech (preview) is=
 currently sharing the same price and SKU ID with Fast Transcription.</p>
                <p class=3D"text-body5"><sup>VL1</sup>With Voice Live Pro, =
developers can choose from larger LLMs such as GPT-Realtime, GPT-4o and GPT=
-4.1 models. With Voice Live Standard, developers can choose from smaller L=
LMs such as GPT-4o-Mini-Realtime, GPT-4o Mini and GPT-4.1 Mini models. With=
 Voice Live Lite, developers can choose from SLMs and equivalent models suc=
h as GPT-4.1 Nano and Phi models. Models for each tier will be updated or r=
etired as they become available. To learn more how Voice Live API pricing w=
orks, click <a href=3D"https://docs.microsoft.com/zh-cn/azure/ai-services/s=
peech-service/voice-live#pricing" aria-label=3D"Learn more about how Voice =
Live API pricing works, including Voice Live Plus, Basic, and Lite model op=
tions" data-bi-an=3D"body" data-bi-tn=3D"undefined">here</a>.</p>
                <p class=3D"text-body5"><sup>VL2</sup>You will be charged s=
eparately for custom speech and custom voice model training and hosting. Re=
fer to the =E2=80=98Speech to Text =E2=80=93 Custom Transcription=E2=80=99 =
and =E2=80=98Text to Speech =E2=80=93 Custom Voice =E2=80=93 Professional=
=E2=80=99 pricing for details. Custom voice is a limited access feature. <a=
 href=3D"https://docs.microsoft.com/zh-cn/azure/ai-services/speech-service/=
custom-neural-voice" aria-label=3D"Learn more about how to create custom vo=
ices with the Text to Speech Custom Voice Professional feature" data-bi-an=
=3D"body" data-bi-tn=3D"undefined">Learn more about how to create custom vo=
ices</a>.</p>
                <p class=3D"text-body5"><sup>LI</sup>This price includes te=
xt output</p>
