ucators can use the capability to evaluate pronunciation of multiple speake=
rs in real time. Visit <a href=3D"https://docs.microsoft.com/zh-cn/azure/co=
gnitive-services/speech-service/pronunciation-assessment-tool?tabs=3Ddispla=
y" aria-label=3D"Visit documentation link to learn more about pronunciation=
 assessment features" data-bi-an=3D"faq-01" data-bi-tn=3D"undefined">docs</=
a> to learn more.
